Localization.AdminAnonymFoldersDescription:
mafoda Nawo / owona - awa mafoda / owona izo popanda wosuta kutsimikizika *, izo zikutanthauza kuti zilipo alendo onse (ngati kugwirizana a). onse ogwiritsa angalenge mafoda zimenezi / owona ku menyu "Share → Pangani kugwirizana pagulu". Komabe, mafoda nawo angakhale ndi zilolezo zochepa pakuti ikukweza, otsitsira, owona / mafoda mndandanda. M'munsimu tebulo limasonyeza kuti mafoda nawo / owona analengedwa ndi owerenga. Ntchito kulumikizana pagulu zimaonetseratu molondola onetsetsani kuti Handlers \ Anonymousdownload.ashx amalola kupeza anonymous kuti IIS. Mukhoza onani ichi pa Diagnostics page. Onetsetsani kuti anonymous wosuta nkhani anatumizidwa Handlers \ Anonymousdownload.ashx ali NTFS kuwerenga / kulemba zilolezo kwa nawo mafoda / owona
*  . &Mdash;   ngati mulibe mwachindunji owerenga, amene yekha analola mwayi.

Localization.AdminUpdateAutoInfo: Mtundu wa kukulitsa ndi makina pafupifupi kwathunthu. Iwo amakhala ndi mapazi 2: kubwerera kwa zoikamo zikusinthira (muyenera kukopera kupulumutsa file kubwerera), unsembe wa Baibulo latsopano ndi kubwezeretsa zoikamo ku wapamwamba kubwerera. HTTP Commander angathe kukuthandizani kukopera mabuku atsopano ndi kukhazikitsa kapena mukhoza mwachindunji njira ndi zipi Archive ndi Baibulo latsopano pa makina athu.
